name: CAVE WRITINGS ON THE WALLS OF THE BLOCKCHAIN

metadata.name: CAVE WRITINGS ON THE WALLS OF THE BLOCKCHAIN : 001
metadata.description: The first cave writing on to the walls of the blockchain is a evolving and devolving. This drawing is also accompanied by music to go along with the drawings transformation of being finished to being unfinished in a loop. The drawing and music is created a by the artist Earn Money.
